n singer and drummer\nBULLET::::- 1985 – Patrice Bergeron, Canadian ice hockey player\nBULLET::::- 1985 – Aries Merritt, American hurdler\nBULLET::::- 1985 – Lukáš Rosol, Czech tennis player\nBULLET::::- 1985 – Eric Wright, American football player\nBULLET::::- 1986 – Natalie Tran, Australian actress, online producer\nBULLET::::- 1987 – Filipe Francisco dos Santos, Brazilian footballer\nBULLET::::- 1987 – Nathan Gerbe, American ice hockey player\nBULLET::::- 1987 – Zack Sabre Jr., English wrestler\nBULLET::::- 1988 – Han Seung-yeon, South Korean singer and dancer\nBULLET::::- 1988 – Nichkhun, Thai-American singer-songwriter and actor\nBULLET::::- 1988 – Ricky Petterd, Australian footballer\nBULLET::::- 1989 – Maurkice Pouncey, American football player\nBULLET::::- 1989 – Kim Tae-hwan, South Korean footballer\nBULLET::::- 1990 – Daveigh Chase, American actress\nBULLET::::- 1990 – Travis Mahoney, Australian swimmer\nBULLET::::- 1991 – Manuel Fischnaller, Italian footballer\nBULLET::::- 1991 – Emily Bett Rickards, Canadian actress\nBULLET::::- 1992 – Dmitry Abyzov, Russian footballer\nBULLET::::- 1992 – Mikaël Kingsbury, Canadian skier\nBULLET::::- 1992 – Mitch Grassi, American singer and songwriter\nBULLET::::- 1994 – Alejandra Álvarez, Ecuadorian tennis player\nBULLET::::- 1995 – Valentine Holmes, Australian rugby league player\nBULLET::::- 1995 – Kyle Kuzma, American basketball player\nBULLET::::- 1997 – Emre Mor, Turkish football player\nBULLET::::- 759 – Oswulf, king of Northumbria\nBULLET::::- 811 – Gao Ying, Chinese politician (b. 740)\nBULLET::::- 946 – Muhammad ibn Tughj al-Ikhshid, Egyptian ruler (b. 882)\nBULLET::::- 1115 – Matilda of Tuscany (b. 1046)\nBULLET::::- 1129 – Emperor Shirakawa of Japan (b. 1053)\nBULLET::::- 1198 – Berthold of Hanover, Bishop of Livonia\nBULLET::::- 1345 – Jacob van Artevelde, Flemish statesman (b. 1290)\nBULLET::::- 1568 – Carlos, Prince of Asturias (b. 1545)\nBULLET::::- 1594 – John Boste, English martyr and saint (b. 1544)\nB